CWO++ library ver 0.31
release date : 20 Feb. 2017
Bug fix:
improved computational accuracy of diffraction calculations and auxiliary functions
mopified all diffraction calculations on GPU.Fixed diffraction calculation on GPU. Calculation sizes other than 2^n can also be calculated.
fixed bugs of random phase functions on GPU
GPU functions were fixed: copy constructor, Average, Variance, DoubleStepFresnel
added SSIM function
added CountNonZero(), ThresholdToZero(float th), ThresholdAbsToZero(float th), ThresholdAbsToZero(float th)
etc....

